14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 34.2, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 34.2. A. Agencies responsible for the collection of
18 monies deposited to the credit of the General Revenue Fund and each
19 of the Special Revenue Funds shall be subject to the provisions of
20 this act. Upon request of the Director of the Office of Management
21 and Enterprise Services, these agencies shall provide the Director
22 of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services an itemized
23 estimate of funds expected to accrue to the General Revenue Fund and
24 each of the Special Revenue Funds for the ensuing fiscal year in the
